        "schemeImageUrl": "",
        "detailedDescription_md": "The Rajasthan Prasuti Sahayata Yojana offers a lifeline to pregnant women from registered construction worker families in the state. Launched by the government, the scheme provides crucial financial support at a critical juncture, aiming to improve the well-being of both mother and child. This assistance empowers women to prioritize their health throughout pregnancy and ensure proper care for their newborns.\n",
        "benefits_md": "\n- The birth of a daughter: ₹ 21,000/-\n- The birth of a son : ₹ 20,000/-\n- In case of not receiving cash benefits under Janani Suraksha Yojana, ₹1,000/- additional assistance will be payable.\n\n",
        "exclusions_md": "<br>\n\n",
